descriptionMarkdown:
Self powered legendary accumulators factory using mostly common items.

Is it needed? Does it solve a real problem? I don't know, but it works, and it was fun to create.

Requirements:
- 4 planets tech (stack inserters, Green belts, heat towers and more) 
- Required Tech: Transport belt capacity (Maxed)
- Most of the items are in common quality. When you see uncommon item, it means "use the best quality you have here, and it should be fine".
- ~200 logistics bots
- Huge Island :)
title: Legendary Accumulators
